{"tid":2182444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你地睇下蘋果呢張相 認唔認得呢位上年好出名既黑警 原來佢就係痱滋警","createTime":"2020-08-31T09:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T11:09:07.000Z","uid":22556,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1b8133e2a675b3686f7b0b52c221878faaee5d7b","tid":2182444,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T09:57:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uH6okGC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuH6okGC.png&h=adbf8675&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去年6月26日大批示威者包圍警察總部，當日有便衣警員聲稱欲往警總上班時遭多人追打，事後有男子被控襲擊傷人及暴動罪。案件早前審結，控辯雙方今早在區域法院結案陳詞。控方稱，如受襲便衣警訛稱傷勢，就不會供出痱滋爆裂的版本，顯示控方證人可信、真誠。而辯方則指，被告當時對便衣警行使合法拘捕權，並指被告被控「13秒的暴動」，而被告只是令警員「爆咗粒痱滋」，質疑「被告有惡意可能性又有幾大呢？」法官郭啟安將於下月17日裁決，並稱如裁定襲擊致造成實際身體傷害罪成，則暴動罪必定成立。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10159407210197448/?extid=RkUZXfz09g1dduG4&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105259197447%2Fposts%2F10159407210197448%2F%3Fextid%3DRkUZXfz09g1dduG4%26d%3Dn&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr0wfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=4ef2727f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10159407210197448/?extid=RkUZXfz09g1dduG4&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"ce01fd26deb0d0b07d2205fd53d61673819b532c","tid":2182444,"uid":245849,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T10:07:24.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n控方稱，如受襲便衣警訛稱傷勢，就不會供出痱滋爆裂的版本，顯示控方證人可信、真誠。<br />\n<br />\n讀法律讀到你個人講嘢咁鳩"},{"pid":"464ae3283b8129ac9027026429a381c568032eaf","tid":2182444,"uid":305602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T11:09:07.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2dt0hDKK130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2dt0hDKK130&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr0wfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=2dedcb2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=